CatDescriptText: A presentation of Native American dance at YMCA gym, Centre Avenue. A man dressed in full costume, including headdress, moccasins, feathers, and loin cloth, plays a drum, and bells (attached to legs) while dancing on stage. An audience of children wearing headdresses watch.
TitMainTitle: Man wearing Native American dress performing dance to audience of children wearing paper feather headbands during father - son jamboree, Centre Avenue YMCA
